# Prompt Routing

## Route through the Orchestrator

Any feature, bug fix, refactor, or multi-step task → invoke the **Orchestrator** subagent. Do not attempt to handle these directly.

## Handle directly in conversation

Quick questions, config tweaks, one-liner changes, or non-code discussions → handle directly without the subagent workflow.
